name: 6 Kings - King Themba
description:
They did not know that spaceships existed in the past, present and future.
That the world is not what it appears to be.
That there is an entire existence watching and protecting us from ourselves.
King Themba has inherited his throne in this space.
He sets a precedent for all future lines.
He honours the change required to move throughout the cosmos unharmed and totally assisted.
Look past the stars. Beyond the milky way.
He is waiting for you there.
